The paper deals with efficient coding schemes for $\sigma$-ary sequences, which involves concepts from information theory (cs.IT), combinatorics (cs.DM), and coding theory (cs.CC). The paper also discusses algorithms for performing the task, which falls under the category of data structures (cs.DS) and computational geometry (cs.CG).
